data.description: Welcome to 901 Chestnut St.  Are you looking for outside relaxation and fun; come and enjoy this 4 bed / 1.5 bath home located close to the river and bike trails.  Sit on your large partially covered deck viewing your, swimming pool all within a fenced in back yard.  This large home/yard has all the living and storage space your growing family will need.  The beautiful stone gas fireplace is a focal point in the living room.  Enjoy your newer low maintenance metal roof and pellet stove.  The 2+ garage with a second story loft is a bonus to keep all of your water toys and cars in.
